BOREDNOMORE3-DOWNLOADER 1 "January 2025" "0.7.0" "BoredNoMore3 Manual"
.SH NAME
borednomore3-downloader \- fetch wallpapers from multiple online sources
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B borednomore3-downloader
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B borednomore3-downloader
downloads high-resolution wallpapers from multiple sources including
Unsplash, Pexels, Pixabay, Picsum, Wallhaven, Google, and Bing.
.PP
Features smart sequential numbering and SHA256 deduplication to prevent
duplicate downloads across sources.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-d " PATH" "\fR, \fB\-\-directory " PATH
Save directory (default: current directory)
.TP
.BI \-s " QUERY" "\fR, \fB\-\-search " QUERY
Search query (default: "dark wallpaper")
.TP
.BI \-n " COUNT" "\fR, \fB\-\-number " COUNT
Number of wallpapers to download (default: 10)
.TP
.B \-D, \-\-deep
Enable deep search (multiple pages)
.TP
.BI \-w " SOURCES" "\fR, \fB\-\-websites " SOURCES
Comma-separated sources: unsplash, pexels, pixabay, picsum, wallhaven, google, bing, all
.TP
.BI \-o " NUMBER" "\fR, \fB\-\-overwrite " NUMBER
Start numbering from specific number (disables duplicate detection)
.TP
.B \-R, \-\-random-source
Randomly select one source
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Display help
.TP
.B \-v, \-\-version
Display version
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B borednomore3-downloader -s "space" -n 20
Download 20 space wallpapers
.TP
.B borednomore3-downloader -w unsplash,pexels -D
Deep search from Unsplash and Pexels
.TP
.B borednomore3-downloader -R -n 50
Download 50 from random source
.SH FILE NAMING
Images saved as: wallpaper_NNNNN.jpg (e.g., wallpaper_00001.jpg)
